{"tid":1461911,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[經濟手段救港] 日五罷買行動正式開放簽署－一定要ＳＩＧＮ　ＵＰ！","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T04:54:33.000Z","uid":58883,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ada3e2f7a0d8d06608e8c418717d1928a96c68a5","tid":1461911,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">＃日五罷買　＃日五罷買救港　# 全民罷買日　＃罷買，我罷得起　＃Sunfribyebuy　 #byebuydayhk ＃２００萬人和理非一直係義士身後支持佢地！</span><br />\n<br />\n響應唔到罷工？遊行出唔到黎？唔敢上前線？去唔到機場？仲有心情買野嗎？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地可以再出多一份力－響應罷買運動！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買運動正式開放宣誓承諾ＳＩＧＮ　ＵＰ！</span></strong></span><br />\n我地需要每一個６１２出黎既２００萬人一齊幫手響應罷買行動。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">簽署ＬＩＮＫ</span></span>　<a href=\"https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbyebuydayhk.github.io%2Fbyebuydayweb%2Fpledge.html&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=4ea2989a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你地係連登仔，和理非，勇武，爸爸媽媽，<span style=\"color: red;\">每一份響應罷買既力量都好緊要</span>！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">ＳＩＧＮ ＵＰ人數</span>好緊要，係我地向政府施壓既籌碼！請大家一定要廣傳，叫哂希望支持運動既親友簽署！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買內容（好簡單）</span></span><br />\n1.      逄星期五、日不花費於日常必須以外的消費<br />\n2.      逄星期五、日不在外食 (上班人士午餐除非可以帶返否則難以避免，但晚餐回家進餐都十分有幫助)<br />\n3.      同時呼籲不光顧抵制清單內的企業，就算買日用品/其他消費都只幫襯良心/本土/外資企業<br />\n4.      呼籲推己及人, 例如絲打比仔仔約逢星期五、日出街食飯，同佢地講逄星期五、日罷買，或只揀良心企業<br />\n由上述基本概念，長遠減低整體消費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解要罷買？</span></span><br />\n政府漠視民意，官黑勾結，利用警黑合作／白色恐怖等下流手段打擊市民言論自由。然而政府對市民傷亡不聞不問，只談經濟，由此可見，經濟係向政府施壓既其中一個有效手段。<span style=\"color: red;\">我地希望令政府唔好再用下流手段，正面回應民間五大訴求。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">罷買可以好有效</span><br />\n如果香港有200萬人=1/4人口每星期少2日購物 = 1/4*2/7 = 少7%營業額，對鋪租貴既香港地，7%營業額分分鍾就等於商家既50%淨利。罷買唔係罷工, 幾個人唔返工對間公司連作可能無影響, 但香港咁多人, 只要集體真係唔買, 生意少左就係少左, 實有效果。<br />\n<br />\n罷買目的係令到香港經濟短期受影響，令社會各界開始不滿政府。更加有學者研究指出，罷買只需要全港252,000人集中一日不消費，經濟就會受到好大影響。 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>(BBC： The '3.5% rule:' How a small minority can change the world.)</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可以支持返良心小店嗎？</span></span><br />\n罷買唔係希望大家苦行，亦唔係希望搞死所有商家。我地會配合其他藍黃店舖ＡＰＰ，呼籲大家將有必要既消費花係良心小店上，同時全面抵制奶共／黑心店。<br />\n長遠黎講我地目標係令到經濟受影響，搞死奶共／黑心店，黃店唔受影響甚至有正面影響。<br />\n自由篩　<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1423228/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1423228/page/1</a><br />\n發夢罷食app　<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1421345/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1421345/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">參與罷買者的好處</span></span><br />\n1.      香港消費貴，養成罷買習慣減低消費，同時能夠建立良好儲蓄習慣<br />\n2.      儲錢捐助立場/其他僅有的中立新聞機構，保護新聞自由<br />\n3.      留錢幫助有需要人士<br />\n4.      留錢買保護裝備<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解揀星期日同五？</span></span><br />\n我地相信一星期揀幾日，會比較容易令香港人持續實行。而星期日同五兩日係由１萬人既投票結果決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人有可能響應嗎？</span></span><br />\n我地揀左每星期日同五　兩日去集體響應。相信呢２個月發生既事，加上互相影響提點下，香港人唔會再善忘。<br />\n<br />\nSo far Facebook/ig都見到好多人share我地既posters，特別係Working Class既反應好好，都成功係爸爸媽媽間廣傳。但係，最緊要都係你既參與同share。<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">（直擊養心殿午市營業狀況：　<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1454146/page/1）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1454146/page/1）</a><br />\n</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未來活動方向 </span></span><br />\na. 陸續推動其他innovative既嚮應方法，如$50/day challenge<br />\nb. 配合其他人搞既活動，例如去商場涼冷氣<br />\nc. 配合其他組織，例如環保組織，共同將罷買概念輸出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfvAQNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfvAQNs.jpg&h=b5fc5a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VaKt3Uh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVaKt3Uh.jpg&h=ee1783ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">FACEBOOK PAGE　<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=34b1dc1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/</a><br />\nIG PAGE　<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=4ca3c82c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/byebuydayhk/</a><br />\n罷買運動文字詳情　<a href=\"https://buyersstrike2019.wixsite.com/mysite\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuyersstrike2019.wixsite.com%2Fmysite&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=21e13c03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buyersstrike2019.wixsite.com/mysite</a><br />\n以前既ＰＯＳＴ　<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441419/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441419/page/1</a><br />\n金水ＦＢ　ＰＯＳＴ　<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/photos/a.233233693430128/2382386658514810/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fphotos%2Fa.233233693430128%2F2382386658514810%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=5f5eb5a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/photos/a.233233693430128/2382386658514810/?type=3&amp;theater</a></span>"},{"pid":"a36e501875afcf1ae93036164e6da3ac36f1b4e4","tid":1461911,"uid":58883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVyZx1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVyZx1R.jpg&h=7a385adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/soO3ffb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsoO3ffb.jpg&h=7802036e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNJCjGR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNJCjGR.jpg&h=2ffbb3b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o5T3ffc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo5T3ffc.jpg&h=b6b0b614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrXC38x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrXC38x.jpg&h=adf4bb59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6nFQEGT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6nFQEGT.jpg&h=87dd22d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wdnb8Ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwdnb8Ad.jpg&h=3be1f6b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vp8F1Ve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvp8F1Ve.jpg&h=cf4ddcdc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6c8cfb1b60a2d12d0125bc3d141f21bfafabea0","tid":1461911,"uid":260897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9fc1674c27dcadc8ab79fa87648fd84bdeaec59a","tid":1461911,"uid":35005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/173837_21ef187a1bdc7521c2e94a6e7a04142f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F20