-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeS2LtDC.png&h=6b939769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"會整呀，　但依家人手唔夠想廣傳左ＩＤＥＡ先，cover埋年紀大Ｄ唔會玩ＣＨＡＬＬＥＮＧＥ　既人先"},{"pid":"d6f22fee23c896c9981b58c365f14d75732e9a22","tid":1461911,"uid":103913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:51:56.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"097ce7de78d2f7e324e02fa89fe27a1cf44e8d80","tid":1461911,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVyZx1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVyZx1R.jpg&h=7a385adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非終極手段：以罷買迫政府回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n日五罷買運動正式開放ＳＩＧＮ ＵＰ！！<br />\n請大家一定要ＳＩＧＮ，人數好緊要<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">詳情</span> <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1461911/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1461911/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">直接簽署ＬＩＮＫ</span><a href=\"https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbyebuydayhk.github.io%2Fbyebuydayweb%2Fpledge.html&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=4ea2989a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html</a><br />\n<br />\n目標：香港市民不滿政府腐敗無能，２００萬人響應罷買行動，ＧＤＰ減少３％，政府被迫回應<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span>"},{"pid":"5fddcf98554371050529d191cf466a3b646ef09d","tid":1461911,"uid":7524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:04:59.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"1d17818c5e3fb564212eccb29c25a80cae42cba4","tid":1461911,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVyZx1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVyZx1R.jpg&h=7a385adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非終極手段：以